description: BrandPilot hackathon MVP rules
alwaysApply: true
---

We are building BrandPilot: from brand DM to published campaign — fully autonomous.

MVP:
A brand reaches out. BrandPilot checks fit, calculates sponsorship rate, negotiates, asks for 50% advance, verifies payment, researches brand/product/creator tone, drafts X + LinkedIn content, spaces it into the creator's organic calendar, gets brand approval, asks for final payment, verifies payment, then marks ready to post.

Hard constraints:
- One creator only.
- One seeded brand deal only.
- No auth.
- No real social posting.
- No multi-user complexity.
- Every agent action must create a visible log.
- Payment gates are mandatory.
- No draft before advance payment.
- No ready-to-post before final payment.
- No external message/post without approval.
- If integrations are missing, use demo adapters.

UI:
Left: WhatsApp-style brand conversation.
Middle: deal pipeline and calendar.
Right: agent log and safety checks.
Bottom: drafts, payment state, scheduled slots.